

**Mash hedai d si shohshonaj g Jesus **

*An g neid g Luke 3:23-38 *

1 Ia atsh mahsi g Jesus Christ jewed dahm k ab d amjedkamaj hegai t‑kekelibad ha‑kownalig mash hab chehgig David. Kush g Davidbad ab d amjedkamaj hegai mash d t‑shohshon ahchim Tutuligo ch hab chehgig Abraham. 

In ant wo oꞌoha g ha‑chechgig hegam mash d Jesus Christ shohshonbad. 

2 Abraham atsh wa an alidt g Isaac. 

Tsh g Isaac an alidt g Jacob. 

Tsh g Jacob an ha aꞌalidt hegam Judah. 

3 Tsh g Judah an ha aꞌalidt g Perez ch Zerah heg ab mash d Tamar. 

Tsh g Perez an alidt g Hezron. 

Tsh g Hezron an alidt g Ram. 

4 Tsh g Ram an alidt g Amminadab. 

Tsh g Amminadab an alidt g Nahshon. 

Tsh g Nahshon an alidt g Salmon. 

5 Tsh g Salmon an alidt g Boaz heg ab mash d Rahab. 

Tsh g Boaz an alidt g Obed heg ab mash d Ruth. 

Tsh Obed an alidt g Jesse. 

6 Tsh g Jesse an alidt g David. 

David atsh an alidt g Solomon heg ab mash d chum hohnigaj g Uriah. 

7 Tsh g Solomon an alidt g Rehoboam. 

Tsh g Rehoboam an alidt g Abijah. 

Tsh g Abijah an alidt g Asa. 

8 Tsh g Asa an alidt g Jehoshaphat. 

Tsh g Jehoshaphat an alidt g Joram. 

Kush ihda Joram d shonaj g Uzziah. 

9 Tsh g Uzziah an alidt g Jodam. 

Tsh g Jodam an alidt g Ahaz. 

Tsh g Ahaz an alidt g Hezekiah. 

10 Tsh g Hezekiah an alidt g Manassah. 

Tsh g Manassah an alidt g Amos. 

Tsh g Amos an alidt g Josiah. 

11 Kush ihda Josiah d ha‑shon hegam Jeconiah matsh eda gam hu hab i e juh g t‑shohshonbad Babylon kihhim wui. 

  

12 Jeconiah atsh an hahawa alidt g Shealtiel. 

Tsh g Shealtiel an alidt g Zerubbabel. 

13 Tsh g Zerubbabel an alidt g Abiud. 

Tsh g Abiud an alidt g Eliakim. 

Tsh g Eliakim an alidt g Azol. 

14 Tsh g Azol an alidt g Zadok. 

Tsh g Zadok an alidt g Akim. 

Tsh g Akim an alidt g Eliud. 

15 Tsh g Eliud an alidt g Eliazar. 

Tsh g Eliazar an alidt g Matthan. 

Tsh g Matthan an alidt g Jacob. 

16 Tsh g Jacob an alidt g Joseph. 

Kush ihda Joseph d kunaj hegai mo d Jesus jeꞌe ch hab chehgig Mary. 

K ihda Jesus hab e aꞌaga Christ. 

17 Pegih, nt gamai giꞌik an oꞌoha g ha‑chechgig hegam mo d e‑oꞌogbad am i amjed mash eda am oimmed g Abrahambad ch am hugkam mash eda am oimmed g Davidbad. Kunt hab waꞌap gamai giꞌik an oꞌoha g ha‑chechgig hegam mo d e‑oꞌogbad heg i amjed ch gam hu hugkam matsh eda gam hu hab i e juh g t‑shohshon Babylon wui. Kunt gamai giꞌik an oꞌoha g ha‑chechgig hegam mo d e‑oꞌogbad heg i amjed ch gam hu hugkam matsh ab mahsi hegai mo hab e aꞌaga Jiosh si Kehsha \(Christ\). 

**Matsh mahsi g Jesus **

*An g neid g Luke 2:1-7 *

18 Ia ant wo oꞌoha matsh has e juh matsh eda mahsi g Jesus Christ. Am amtsh i apꞌech matsh idam Joseph ch Mary wo e hohont. Tsh am hahawa s‑e mai mat g ali wo bei. 19 K hab chuꞌig g chehanig mat chum pi wo ha bei g cheoj matp hab wo wa e juh. Kush g Joseph am wabsh si s‑ap oid g chehanig ch hekaj hab e elid mat pi wo be k wabshaba pi hedai wo ha ahgi. T hab pi wo si e el g Mary. 

20 Sh am oidahim ihda g Joseph. Kutsh am haha wabsh ab wui i e chehgi g anghil am chehchkij ed k hab kaij, “Joseph map ab d Davidbad amjedkam, am g wabsh s‑ap e tahtk k wo bei g Mary mat d wo m‑wehm kihkamk. Hekia S‑apꞌekam Gewkdag at hab juh ihda ali mat g Mary wo bei. 21 Kut d wo cheojk. Kupt hab wo chehch Jesus mo hab d ahga ha‑Doꞌibiakam. Bat wo chehgigk nat pi wo ha doꞌibia g e‑hemajkamga ab ha‑chuꞌijig amjed.” Neh, bash kaij g anghil am Joseph wui. 

22 Wehs atsh wa hab e juh ihda hab masma mash wa hab masma heki hu hab kaij g Jiosh. Kelibad Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam atki an oꞌoha mash wa hab kaij: 

23 Hema g si s‑ap chehia at wo bei g cheoj ali pi koi ab hu i miabidk g cheoj. 

Kumt hab wo aꞌagad Manuel mo hab d ahga Jiosh o t‑Wehmaj. *Isaiah 7:14 * 

24 Kutsh hekid am i nea g Joseph k atsh am ha hekaj hab e juh mash has i kaij g anghil ab wui matsh an bei g Mary. 25 Sh wabshaba pi am hu hab masma e wehm kih mo g e wehm kihkam am hugkam mat hekid ip bei g ali. Tsh g Joseph hab hahawa chehch Jesus. 

